<h2 id="_2-brdf-测量" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-brdf-测量" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2.BRDF 测量</h2>
<h3 id="_1-基于图像的-brdf-测量" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-基于图像的-brdf-测量" aria-hidden="true">#</a> [1]基于图像的 BRDF 测量</h3>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/e85ac795619a4de69efa5ebf74396ff3.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p>测量BRDF：GonioreReTectometer</p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/750f18ae5ade46469df892b87aa7af7a.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p>一般的做法：</p>
<div class="language-text ext-text line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>foreach outgoing direction wo
    move light to illuminate surface with a thin beam from wo
    for each incoming direction wi
        move sensor to be at direction wi from surface
        measure incident radiance
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><p>效率提升方式：</p>
<ul>
<li>所以各向同性曲面性质将维数从4D 降低到3D</li>
<li>可以利用光路可逆性减少一半测量量</li>
</ul>
